<br>
Thats all I can do to help.  My wife is the faction wis and she could help ya more.  Just send Scratchy a tell in game and she can share some FP and Neriak info with ya...she is ogre though and we havint mastered the great language of troll yet.<br>
<br>
Ichi <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=dalninil>Dalninil</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 104<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/14/02 4:40:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1115.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Stupid Newbie Question - totally OOC post</span><hr size=1> I've seen trolls in neriak...<br>
<br>
If your faction is as messed up as mine ( i think it's more messed up )<br>
<br>
Think Grobb, Neriak, the outpost in OT, and whatever faction city you pick for Velius, and the nexus.<br>
<br>
It's actually kind of a trip, all your goody friends are like I can't kill this or I can't kill that because of faction... well bah on faction just remember the names of those that kill you and some day they will be xp !!!!!<br>
<br>
Oh with enough killing it's possible to bank in High Pass if you're worried about the old world.<br>
<br>
Same with Painelle, Erudin, and Cabilis<br>
<br>
Walk slowly and con everything !<br>
<br>
Dalninil Venorsh<br>
Dark Elf worshiper of Inny and his slave as well ! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ubjond.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bjond</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 163<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/14/02 4:58:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1115.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> For Neriak ..</span><hr size=1> .. you are probably OK in the foreign quarter and to the outer guards.  For the inner, that would depend on your religion mostly.  You can fix Neriak with the red-wine quest -- about 20p made my human (agnostic) monk at least dubious to all the guards.  Guilds will likely hate you (and me) forever, though.  Be very careful and /con the NPCs around the guilds before you approach them.  I had an inky wizard that was born dubious to many in Neriak -- it's not a town that is known for religious tolerance.<br>
<br>
FP -- trolls are KOS (fix with Groflah &amp; tonics or letter delivery -- use tunnels to get to the boat).  Qeynos, KOS (fix in HPH, gnoll ears or Karanas bandit sashes).  Karanas people, KOS (fix in HPH, gnolls).  Rivervale, KOS (fix with Honeybugger &amp; bandages).  Oggok, KOS in parts (/con stuff! hard to fix).  SFG, KOS (fix with tons of BB gnolls).  Halas, KOS (fix with lots of partnered invis-questing -- v. hard to do).  Kelethin, KOS (fix guards with FP muffins to Pandos, merchants not possible).  Felwithe, KOS (can't fix).  Kaladim, KOS (fix with aqua gobs or runneye gobs).  Akanon, KOS (fixable, but I forgot how &amp; why).  Cabalis, KOS (fix with invis-partnered bone-chip quest or old-sebilis kills).  Erudin, KOS (v.hard to fix .. some invis-partnered inside erudin or kill up in Warrens then kill necros then more Warrens, etc.).  Paineel, not sure (kill in Warrens for easy fix).<br>
<br>
I'm not sure about Vellious or Luclin things.  For Vel, my old char just killed all coldain dwarfs and went pro-giant faction.  Giants have the best quest armor, most convenient city for binding, and leave you free to hunt the annoying little dwarfs and lucrative dragons.  The coldain city dwarfs drop some very nice (almost hate-plane quality) armor for melees, too. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/utwotribes.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Twotribes</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Board Troll</span><br>  Posts: 199<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/14/02 6:20:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1115.topic&index=4>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Stupid Newbie Question - totally OOC post</span><hr size=1> In Neriak, the one VERY dangerous place is the Home of the Necro/Shadowknight Guild. There are Ghouls guarding the entrance to this area. They are solely on the necro/sk guild faction. Believe me the wine quest wont raise faction with them.<br>
<br>
As a troll or ogre you are probably initially dubious with the ghouls. But before getting close con them.  You can mess faction up with individual guilds also.  Learn where they are and who is on the guild faction.<br>
<br>
Freeport (east) underground is generally safe for troll/ ogre, except they added a necro (female human I believe) that seems to hate my Rallos Zek SK Ogre. She is in a Cul De Sac so I can still reach Venders and trainers. <br>
<br>
Never been to Painell, but I suspect that intial faction is KOS. Cabilis is KOS to all non Iksar till faction work is done.  Over there outpost and ogre village in Timerous Deep are not intially KOS to evil type races. They are on Venril Sather alignment. If you hunt in Karnors, Kaesora, Charisis (howling Stone) you will lose faction.<br>
<br>
Ogguk is ok for a troll, as Grobb is ok for an Ogre. Be warned though..... The Shadowknight Guilds do not like each other. Quests in Greenblood (ogre) SK guild will lower faction with Nightshade (or night something) (troll) SK Guild and vic verse. And the neriak Necro/SK guild will tolerate but not train nor sell to Troll or Ogre.<br>
<br>
Unknown by me is the status of the Ogre Shaman guild towards the Troll SK quests. Ogre Shaman also worship Rallos Zek.<br>
<br>
Dark Elves have ita little easier, No initial troll or Ogre faction is less than Dubious and except for certain NPC's in West and East Freeport (also the magic guilds area and probably warrior as well) they can wander those zones. North Freeport is a little trickery, but easily fixed if you are KOS there.<br>
<br>
Also Troll and Ogre are intitially KOS in High Pass as well, but that is fixed by killing orcs or gnolls in the pass (or the few higher level ones in Kith and EKarana) or by killing the Raiders on the river in North and South Karana. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ubufferofnewbies.showPublicProfile?language=EN>BufferofNewbies</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/14/02 10:41:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1115.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Stupid Newbie Question - totally OOC post</span><hr size=1> The Ghouls in Neriak are on their own faction NeriakGhoul (killed one once to find out for sure). <br>
There is NO KNOWN way of raiseing that faction, just lowering it. The are KoS to <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  ANY </b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> non-Dark Elf. <br>
If you must get past them to the guild, use Invis. to Undead. it works wonders. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Of course, as a Paladin.. I dont think i would have to worry about it.<br>
<br>
/role<br>
<br>
'As well you should be hated you vile beast! I shall cleanse the lands of your stench.' <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ubjond.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bjond</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 170<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/15/02 12:05:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1115.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Eh, Grobb is ..</span><hr size=1> .. not safe for all teir'dal.  Both grobb and oggok have religious guards (as does neriak).  If you're not agnostic, be very very careful. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uartillis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Artillis</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 191<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/15/02 4:37:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1115.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Eh, Grobb is ..</span><hr size=1> In regaurds to your wanting to travel.  <br>
<br>
The only race you could have picked MORE hated then a troll would have been Iksar.<br>
<br>
If you are someone who wants freedom to roam I'd recomend a different race. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/utwotribes.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Twotribes</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Board Troll</span><br>  Posts: 201<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/15/02 8:59:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1115.topic&index=8>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Stupid Newbie Question - totally OOC post</span><hr size=1> Ghouls in 3rd Gate are NOT kill on sight to my Ogre SK.  They are KOS to my Erud SK though. Never had a troll SK , but I suspect that as ogre they are dubious to the ghouls.  <br>
<br>
At least this was true several months ago, been at least that long since Grong was in 3rd Gate, not a lot there for him since the SK guild wont talk to him. ANd he couldnt get any of the quests to raise his faction in the Guild area.<br>
<br>
Also, on the line of Grobb and Ogguk, I have yet to be attacked by any of the guilds there as a Dark Elf (worship Innorruuk) SK. BUT your right, you have to watch where you are, individual factions do change and there are a couple Single NPC's on their own strange factions. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=1115.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=1115.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1115.topic&index=8><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.threadControl?topicID=1115.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1115.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1115.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub94.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="firionaviefrm1">Firiona Vie General Chat<option value="firionaviefrm2">The Market Square<option value="firionaviefrm4">The Soapbox<option value="firionaviefrm6">Signature Testing<option value="firionaviefrm7">Patch Message